qMetaDef.title: Sales & Margin Analysis
qMetaDef.description: View sales and margin data by state, region, and product.

qStringExpression.qExpr: ='Sales $ by Product Group (sorted by Budget Amt)'

qAttributeExpressions.qExpression: if(((sum([YTD Sales Amount])-sum([LY YTD Sales Amount]))/sum([LY YTD Sales Amount]))<0.05, red(255))

qStringExpression.qExpr: 'Central Sales vs Margin' & ' (Sales '& num(Sum({$<[Region Name]={"Central"}>} [Sales Quantity]*[Sales Price]), '$#,##0;($#,##0)') &')'
'Northeast Sales vs Margin' & ' (Sales '& num(Sum({$<[Region Name]={"Northeast"}>} [Sales Quantity]*[Sales Price]), '$#,##0;($#,##0)') &')'
'Southern Sales vs Margin'& ' (Sales '& num(Sum({$<[Region Name]={"Southern"}>} [Sales Quantity]*[Sales Price]), '$#,##0;($#,##0)') &')'
'Western Sales vs Margin'& ' (Sales '& num(Sum({$<[Region Name]={"Western"}>} [Sales Quantity]*[Sales Price]), '$#,##0;($#,##0)') &')'
